1. DESIGN FILES — CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 – Weakly Reciprocal
   (SPDX: CERN-OHL-W-2.0)

   Applies to the parametric design and everything from which a physical
   sambuca can be made. Specifically:

     - cad/                      (SolidWorks parts, equations file, design table)
     - drawings/                 (SVGs, manufacturing drawings)
     - cnc/                      (CNC operation plans)
     - harness/                  (harness assembly designs)
     - bom.csv
     - sourcing.csv
     - cut-list.csv
     - validation.csv
     - family-spec.csv

   See LICENSE-design.txt for the full license text, or:
   https://spdx.org/licenses/CERN-OHL-W-2.0.html

